  <h2>
    Validation Process
  </h2>

  <p>
    While implementing the Feature Validation Process, we realized our existing 
    experiment-calling process wasn't suitable for early decision-making. To 
    address this, I adapted a framework called Stop, Pivot, Preserve. It drove 
    accountability, fast decision-making, and pushed squad leads to treat their 
    leads as investors. Weekly, squad leads made investment recommendations and 
    aligned with their leads. This, combined with our feature validation 
    process, accelerated progress and reduced risks.
  </p>
</article>

